dct_description_sm: prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center, Washington, D.C.
Relief shown by contours, shading, and spot heights.
Sheets separately titled and numbered, e.g. Stockerau, 40; Deutsch Wagram, 41; Wien, 59; etc.
Local holdings sheets are from editions 6 and 7.
Includes glossary, index to adjoining sheets, boundaries diagram, DMA logo, notes, and text.
Most text, glossary, and legend in English, German, and Italian.
